snippet.title: (Official) COGEN: Sword of Rewind - Official 3rd Trailer. Release date set!!
snippet.description:
"Rewind Time, Forge Ahead!"
Fight, Die, Rewind
Sword Action like you’ve Never Felt Before!

DLC collaboration with "Gunvolt Chronicles: Luminous Avenger iX 2" coming soon!

■Release Date
January 27th, 2022

■Platform
Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Steam
*Physical version only available for Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4

■Price
Digital: USD 24.99 / EUR 24.99
Physical: TBD

■Composer
Motoi Sakuraba

■Official Site
https://cogen.city/en/
https://twitter.com/Gemdrops_EN

©Unity Technologies Japan / Gemdrops, Inc.
